{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, she was evaluated by the infectious disease team and was started on antibiotic treatment with vancomycin.",
    "A PICC line was placed, and she continued IV vancomycin treatment for six weeks.",
    "During that time, additional sensitivity analysis was performed, and the sensitivity of the organisms to minocycline was demonstrated.",
    "Therefore, her PICC line was removed, and oral treatment with minocycline was initiated, with a plan for at least six months of treatment.",
    "MRI completed two months postoperatively showed postoperative changes from the arachnoid cyst fenestration, with a small residual cystic fluid collection."
  ]
}